      <title>美联储官员准备降息之际，鲍威尔表示将进行战略评估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/powell-nods-to-upcoming-strategy-review-as-fed-prepares-to-cut-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周末，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在杰克逊霍尔概述了未来几个月的两个优先事项：保持美国经济运转，同时也仔细审视过去几年出了什么问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/powell-nods-to-upcoming-strategy-review-as-fed-prepares-to-cut-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使日元版人民币崩溃，人民币套利交易仍可繁荣发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/yuan-carry-trade-can-prosper-even-after-yen-version-collapsed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月，随着日元飙升，广受欢迎的日元套利交易一蹶不振。这种策略的知名度较低，可能更能抵御此类冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/yuan-carry-trade-can-prosper-even-after-yen-version-collapsed</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
