    <item>
      <title>土耳其最高银行家预计降息周期将于 11 月开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/turkey-s-top-banker-sees-rate-cut-cycle-starting-in-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其最大的私营银行首席执行官表示，土耳其央行很可能在今年晚些时候开始新一轮降息，到 2025 年底借贷成本可能减半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/turkey-s-top-banker-sees-rate-cut-cycle-starting-in-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 07:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特电信股价因股息上涨而创 2008 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/saudi-telecom-jumps-most-since-2014-after-boosting-its-dividend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯最大的电信公司宣布计划提高季度股息并表示可能考虑通过特别支付的方式向投资者提供更多资金后，其股价创下近 16 年来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/saudi-telecom-jumps-most-since-2014-after-boosting-its-dividend</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 07:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚养老金基金将收购州政府 Powerco 股份：AFR</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/australia-pension-fund-to-acquire-state-s-stake-in-powerco-afr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《澳大利亚金融评论报》报道，澳大利亚第二大养老基金澳大利亚退休信托基金同意收购新西兰能源分销商 Powerco 有限公司的多数股权，但并未透露该基金从何处获得此消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/australia-pension-fund-to-acquire-state-s-stake-in-powerco-afr</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 05:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度改革政府工作人员养老金制度，实行固定支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/india-revamps-government-worker-pensions-with-guaranteed-payout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度将实施新的养老金制度，保证联邦政府工作人员退休后可获得其基本工资的一定比例作为退休金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/india-revamps-government-worker-pensions-with-guaranteed-payout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 04:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大劳工委员会要求铁路员工复工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/canada-labor-board-orders-rail-employees-back-to-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大一个独立法庭命令该国两大铁路公司的工人重返工作岗位，并接受具有约束力的仲裁，以解决困扰北美供应链的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/canada-labor-board-orders-rail-employees-back-to-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 22:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储青睐的价格指标将强化降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/world-economy-fed-s-preferred-price-gauge-to-reinforce-rate-cut-prospects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来一周的美国通胀数据将强化人们期待已久的降息即将到来这一信号，而消费者支出数据则表明央行已成功保持经济扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/world-economy-fed-s-preferred-price-gauge-to-reinforce-rate-cut-prospects</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
